For it to work you need to install these:

  pip install speech_recognition 

  pip install pyttsx3

  pip install pyaudio
  
  
Moreover you need to install Flac this is how:

  Windows: You can download and install the FLAC codec from the official website right here: https://xiph.org/flac/download.html 
  
  MacOS: You can install the FLAC codec using Homebrew by running the following command in your Terminal: brew install flac
  
  Linux: You can install the FLAC codec using the package manager and the command is: sudo apt-get install flac
  
  


